    </h2>
  
  
      <div class="meta">
              <div class="submitted">
          Submitted by Mark Baars on Thu, 2012-02-09 08:56        </div>
      
              <div class="terms terms-inline"> in <ul class="links inline"><li class="taxonomy_term_4 first last"><a href="/taxonomy/term/4" rel="tag" title="News and announcements
">News and Announcements</a></li>
</ul></div>
          </div>
  
  <div class="content">
    <p>SpringSource has launched 7 new Hot Seat promotions for the number one Spring Framework class: Core Spring. If you register by March 01, you can <b>SAVE 30%</b> on the following Spring classes:</p>
<ul>
